Articles.Content: If my dell does not open the cheat meneu what do i do
what do you type for cheat menu? is it alt+f12? it works on my asus.
Try alt+fn+f12. Alt+f12 doesn't work for me, but alt+fn+f12 does.

Yeah, some laptops deactivate the function keys by default, and put custom stuff on them instead. Or, they assign the function keys as secondaries to other keys (like the numbers). Gotta make sure the button you press is actually registering as F12, and not as something else.
